exports[`deriveBom golden output (pre-22b refactor contract) > minimal shared fixture (no segments, no site works) 1`] = `
"Modules | Adani Solar ELAN Shine 540 | 540Wp Mono PERC · ALMM · DCR | 8 | nos | 12420 | measured | true | false | 8 enabled panels on canvas
Inverter | GoodWe GW5000-NS | 5kW · 1φ · 2 MPPT | 1 | nos | 55000 | measured | true | false | Selected in Components step
Electrical BOS | DC Solar Cable 4 sq.mm | 4 sq.mm Cu · 1.1kV, UV-resistant, red+black pair | 83 | m | 68 | estimated | true | false | ESTIMATE — 1 strings × module-to-module + 15 m home run × 2 conductors, floored at 30 m (reads HIGH: it charges for module links the panel leads already cover). Place the inverter (Step 6 → Mount inverter), then Auto string, to route the real runs.
Electrical BOS | AC Cable | 3-core 6 sq.mm Cu | 25 | m | 210 | assumed | true | false | ASSUMED 25 m allowance — no meter/service entry placed, so this run cannot be measured. Place it (Step 6 → Mount inverter → Meter) or edit the quantity to the surveyed length.
Electrical BOS | MC4 Connector Pairs | 1000V 30A | 6 | pairs | 95 | derived | true | false | 1 strings × 2 + 4 spare
Electrical BOS | DCDB | 1-in 2-out, fuses + Type-II SPD | 1 | nos | 6100 | derived | true | false | One per inverter, sized from string count
Electrical BOS | ACDB | 32A MCB + Type-II SPD | 1 | nos | 7400 | derived | true | false | AC current 22A × 1.25 safety
Electrical BOS | Conduit + Cable Tray | 25mm HDPE / GI tray | 67 | m | 55 | estimated | true | false | ESTIMATE — DC runs not routed yet: 42 m implied + 25 m AC allowance
Electrical BOS | Net Meter + Generation Meter | DISCOM-approved bidirectional | 1 | set | 9700 | derived | true | false | Required for net metering
Mechanical BOS | Mounting Structure (elevated RCC) | HDG steel, 10° tilt legs + purlins | 8 | panel-set | 950 | derived | true | false | 8 loose/unsegmented FLAT-RCC panels × structure share (pitched faces are billed flush hardware instead). Structural design subject to certified engineer verification (IS 875 wind load, roof capacity, anchoring).
Mechanical BOS | Mounting Rail | Al 6005-T5 40×40 | 19 | m | 320 | derived | true | false | 8 unsegmented flat-RCC/ground/pitched-roof panels × panel length × 1.05 waste
Mechanical BOS | Mid + End Clamps | Al with SS hardware | 24 | nos | 38 | derived | true | false | 8 panels × 2 + ends
Mechanical BOS | Fasteners & Chemical Anchors | SS304 kit | 1 | kit | 1800 | derived | true | false | Per site kit (wiring/misc — structure anchors counted separately)
Safety | Earthing Pits | Chemical earthing, 3m electrode | 2 | nos | 2650 | assumed | true | false | 2 system (DC + AC) (no arrester ⇒ no LPS pit) — ASSUMED convention; electrode count depends on measured soil resistivity (IS 3043), engineer to confirm
Safety | Earthing Strip / Wire | GI 25×3 + 6 sq.mm Cu | 36 | m | 92 | assumed | true | false | 2 runs × 3 m roof height + 30 m ASSUMED interconnect allowance
Safety | Danger Boards & Signage | CEIG-compliant set | 1 | kit | 950 | derived | true | false | Per site kit
Civil & Misc | Installation & Commissioning | Labour, testing, net-meter liaison | 4.3 | kW | 2500 | derived | true | false | 4.3 kWp × ₹2500/kW
Civil & Misc | Transport & Handling | To site | 1 | lot | 6000 | derived | true | false | Lumpsum"
`;

